{"tid":2101674,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"DBS 黑心老細Elizxxxxx cheng","createTime":"2020-07-10T03:28:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T17:22:31.000Z","uid":244914,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"55d037af5475783dd9c913685aa653aa2be63b76","tid":2101674,"uid":244914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T03:28:08.000Z","msg":"勸大家冇咩事都係唔好入dbs做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽個friend講Pb個條kyc team好慘<br />\n佢哋話今年嚟咗個新老細叫Elizxxxxx cheng，一嚟就大執佢地條team，成條team走咗好似成6,7個人，有人自己辭職，有人俾人炒，聽講仲會用手段俾迫人走。跟住又轉佢自己鐘意嘅contractor做perm (佢好似做咗好短時間但好識擦鞋 話之前老細唔受佢呢套本身仲想唔續佢) <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最賤係佢嚟咗一個月都冇就開始炒人。用盡一切方法整走唔鍾意嘅人，幾黑心先會喺而家呢個時期炒個perm staff，人地成頭家要養。聽講俾人炒嗰個做嘢係一般嘅，不過重點係佢炒完人仲要周圍唱<span class=\"xx-large\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n傳到成個office幾條team都知，完全無employee confidentiality，做呢啲位都唔識收下把口。其實dbs不嬲都無炒人嘅文化，就算呢個時期都係freeze下headcount，起碼唔係好似大貓銀行咁。<br />\n<br />\nE成日想帶自己啲人入嚟，日日都掛住搞headcount問題。係好多老細都會想帶自己人過檔，但佢地條team長期都唔夠人做野，個個月都俾人捽數捽到痴線，仲掛住搞依啲19嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地team啲contractor仲慘，日日就提心吊膽驚俾佢針對驚佢唔續約，一係就真係等俾佢迫走。<br />\n<br />\nDbs呢間嘢真係特別多嘢，之前ibg又閪，真係諗清楚都唔好入呢間公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09b8dc12f9934d8eb8e42364061f45d6bf9865c4","tid":2101674,"uid":96095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T03:29:17.000Z","msg":"咁巴打走左未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6db0d74a411d4fa5cfb04a5bb6e0b9bc3aacdca9","tid":2101674,"uid":281701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T10:29:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"971956faf54575ba4c2524a5eb9e9c5f4ce36584","tid":2101674,"uid":281701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T10:29:50.000Z","msg":"點解呢間公司咁架"},{"pid":"d3d23e3baa11b8f5946ce2e91595c4ccc0e3a770","tid":2101674,"uid":126100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"971956faf54575ba4c2524a5eb9e9c5f4ce36584","tid":2101674,"uid":281701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T10:29:50.000Z","msg":"點解呢間公司咁架"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T12:33:32.000Z","msg":"玻仔公司文化好西，D人又冇禮貌"},{"pid":"96009fdcd47cefd99250a52153b07e58a122c258","tid":2101674,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T12:34:40.000Z","msg":"佢個名叫做陳庭佳"},{"pid":"16395970720eb6599f338c95f5c0193909b0770d","tid":2101674,"uid":215706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T12:35:38.000Z","msg":"屌  咁都唔開全名  咁撚驚青抵你比人恰啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"677ae9216329aeb31a2663bef07fccd929c355c4","tid":2101674,"uid":96662,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T12:36:54.000Z","msg":"呢排DBS好紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc4823b62524ffccb01de0b8b315762389f60b2e","tid":2101674,"uid":109428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T13:08:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5d6e4da40f2e5d3791ed58c6caab442d789a01e","tid":2101674,"uid":244914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09b8dc12f9934d8eb